sg":"屌大屎佛<br />\n拍拍拍"},{"pid":"39ec3668184c45ec2ccd5c96e368544f9e9b0f48","tid":987913,"uid":18772,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5084b978d592856cbd0907f2708fd20507dab78e","tid":987913,"uid":64009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3d3a00c921152cc80d32afc1fda8cd83226e6200","tid":987913,"uid":18772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:54:21.000Z","msg":"同欣宜結婚有棟2千萬既樓落你同名共有<br />\n肯唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:59:04.000Z","msg":"我買多棟比佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20140625/large/25ec1p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20140625%2Flarge%2F25ec1p2.jpg&h=31b8d023&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67af6db8506acf369d06feead4a7acf6a57f0a2e","tid":987913,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d06030ace837571cce20e3f8c884aacbaca8394","tid":987913,"uid":38904,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:03:27.000Z","msg":"大部份肥到成座山咁嘅肥婆，條頸後面都好多老泥，因為佢哋沖涼嘅時候卒唔到。&nbsp;<br />\n老泥俾頸部脂肪一層層夾住，日復日年復年咁累積。&nbsp;所以大部份肥婆條頸都係黑色，越黑老泥越厚。&nbsp;如果你哋有幸溝到肥婆，就人一世物一世點都要試下。首先用手指濕少少水起勢咁卒，用匙羹刮出嚟，加兩滴美極慢慢品嚐。&nbsp;初哥可能話核突，但你唔食肥婆老泥等於登上白雲山唔食山水豆腐花一樣咁傻的嗎。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n下身方面又係有學問，肥婆食咁多漢堡包同牛肉，男性荷爾蒙分泌過盛。&nbsp;所以塊西至屎o全部都係毛，無論佢幾乾淨，都有陣咸魚溝變壞乳酪嘅味道。&nbsp;據英國研究，82.5%肥婆都唔會剃腳毛，因為烏低身嗰下等於做sit up，有違肥人忠旨。&nbsp;所以肥婆啲腳毛永遠好似鐵線咁粗。奶西嘅時候叫佢瞓低你忠個頭埋去，兩隻手要掃佢隻腳啲鐵線等佢起雞皮，然後叫佢嗰對火腿夾實自己個頭唔好比空氣流出。&nbsp;陣咸魚味喺真空環境會得到昇華，係有層次而漸進的。奶嗰時攝攝聲，有3D立體音響加回音效果。&nbsp;你嗅覺，味覺，觸覺，聽覺得到前所未有嘅享受，呢啲先叫人生啊。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪嗰part唔多講，因為肥婆塊田多肉好撞係常識，你塞咗入去會感受到溫暖同安全感，比一層一層肉緊緊包住。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n成日笑肥婆以為自己好識食嗰啲人，根本就係未夠班，自以為是嘅表現。你比食女界嘅高手揀減肥前欣宜定係整容後楊怡，佢完全唔想答你，一嚟佢唔想笑勁你問無聊野，二嚟佢已經諗緊點班支美極返嚟。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:10:38.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386802120f529f4bf527165a5c5c7983fd61776d","tid":987913,"uid":4349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b40e1537fe90f756037f811274f96047b2b703bb","tid":987913,"uid":3482,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"e24b420fc37e27c19ebd20b8f622ee55854c0f52","tid":987913,"uid":161709,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"quote":{"pid":"ebbcf6a8e32c8aad443151a356f7a1a5e44fef05","tid":987913,"uid":152840,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T04:23:55.000Z","msg":"catgirl"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T04:29:16.000Z","msg":"catgirl又懶惰又濕疹又核突<br />\n點揀都係欣宜先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T04:41:00.000Z","msg":"欣宜對波冇噤撚肉酸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"1定要揀, 我會自殺<br />\n癡撚線先會揀"},{"pid":"7a3219a68dddd41d118b91144181a7f58a578a37","tid":987913,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97c761b1941d60fc20c924fcce42b396732fc527","tid":987913,"uid":3189,"like":145,"dislike":1,"score":144,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:44:36.000Z","msg":"好認真咁講<br />\n邊個直男會想同欣宜咁親密呀......<br />\n個男仔gay味好濃<br />\n當欣宜係姊妹啫<br />\n就好似鏗鏗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:33:46.000Z","msg":"星夢時代啫"},{"pid":"4afd4a1395684da370441ee1eb4c66b9ba173db5","tid":987913,"uid":143582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"386802120f529f4bf527165a5c5c7983fd61776d","tid":987913,"uid":4349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b40e1537fe90f756037f811274f96047b2b703bb","tid":987913,"uid":3482,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"e24b420fc37e27c19ebd20b8f622ee55854c0f52","tid":987913,"